    <bcl:section id="d2e32" toc="false">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Relationship between tax rates for different property
        classes</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>For taxes imposed under section 388Â <in:desc>[regional district tax collection in electoral areas]</in:desc> of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/r15001_00" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Local Government Act</in:doc></bcl:link>, the relationships between tax rates, expressed as
        ratios of the rate on each property class to the rate on Class 1, must be as set out in the
        following Schedule:</bcl:text>
